#

Pork Tenderloin with Mushroom Sauce and Creamy Mashed Potatoes

$18.5
600 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeNut-Free

Tags:

Comfort FoodGourmetMain Course

Description

Succulent pork tenderloin topped with a rich mushroom sauce and served alongside creamy mashed potatoes, perfect for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • Pork Tenderloin: 1 lb
  • Fresh Champignon Mushrooms: 8 oz
  • Yellow Onion: 1 medium
  • Garlic Cloves: 2
  • Heavy Cream: 1 cup
  • Butter: 4 tbsp
  • Potatoes: 2 lbs
  • Fresh Dill: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
